Package: nirs4all
Title: Portable 'nirs4all' Aggregate Binding
Version: 0.2.5
Authors@R: c(
    person("Gregory", "Beurier", email = "gregory.beurier@cirad.fr", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("nirs4all", "contributors", role = c("ctb", "cph")))
Description: Provides the R package surface for the 'nirs4all-core' aggregate.
    It records the formats, IO, datasets, methods, 'dag-ml', and 'dag-ml-data'
    domains, lazily reaches R upstream packages when they exist, and delegates
    the portable methods subset at run time. Domains without an R binding remain
    metadata-only; no parsing, numerical, or pipeline logic is reimplemented.
License: CeCILL-2.1 | AGPL (>= 3)
URL: https://nirs4all.org, https://github.com/GBeurier/nirs4all-core
BugReports: https://github.com/GBeurier/nirs4all-core/issues
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    yaml
Suggests:
    nirs4allformats,
    nirs4allio,
    nirs4alldatasets,
    n4m,
    dagmldata
